Naaaah. See Michael Meyers, while evil in his own right, is still fallable. He still feels physical sensations. He can be hurt and even killed. Jason is unfeeling. Both emotionally amd physically.[/bq]

>Michael Myers
>He feels physical sensations
>Can be killed
>Implying Michael hasn't been shooted many times (one of them was a direct shoot in the head), being stabbed, survived a explosion, survived even after his head being smashed many times with a large pipe, crushed by a car, decapitated, hanged and even electrocuted.

Even Jason can be "killed" and get hurt, but is unstoppable. Like Michael
Michael _maybe_ can feel and even knows that is killing innocent people, but that doesn't mean he can be stopped.
People even thinks that Michael is even more evil than Jason, judging by the fact that Jason is just a big and disturbing child.
